title: Kamala Harris meeting with Poland's President after US rejects Polish proposal to get jets to Ukraine - CNN

description: Vice President Kamala Harris is meeting with Polish President Andrzej Duda in Warsaw on Thursday, where she's tasked with smoothing over a relationship with a key ally after the US rejected Poland's surprise proposal to facilitate the transfer of its Soviet-era fighter jets to Ukraine.
